Origin
------

Floodilka is a fork of Fluxer (https://github.com/fluxerapp/fluxer),
originally created by Hampus Kraft and the Fluxer Contributors. Fluxer is
licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License version 3 by Fluxer
Platform AB.

The Floodilka project was forked from Fluxer in March 2026. Subsequent
modifications were made by Floodilka Contributors and are also licensed under
AGPLv3.

