Source code
-----------

The complete corresponding source code for the Floodilka web client, desktop
client, and server-side components is available at:

  https://github.com/Floodilka/Floodilka-Web

This source repository satisfies the requirements of AGPLv3 sections 6 and 13
for code that is conveyed in binary form and for code that is interacted with
remotely over a network.

Mobile clients
--------------

The Floodilka iOS and Android mobile clients are independent works authored
from scratch by Floodilka Contributors and are not derived from Fluxer or any
AGPLv3-licensed code. They are distributed under their own proprietary
license, separate from this repository.

The mobile clients connect to AGPLv3-licensed Floodilka server components
over a network protocol; per AGPLv3 section 13, source code for the server
components is made available at the URL above.

